---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Cara Colgate, LICSW" currentPage="home">
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-path.jpg"
      alt="A winding wooden boardwalk through green marshland under a dramatic sky"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>
      When we feel deeply connected and understood, we can live more
      authentically and joyfully. But when we feel stuck or conflicted, clarity
      can seem out of reach. With over 25 years of experience, I help clients
      work through challenges, heal from the past, and shift from simply doing
      to truly being — clear, connected, and engaged in life. I specialize in
      supporting individuals and families who find themselves at a crossroads,
      whether in their relationships, careers, or ways of living. In my
      relationship work, I help partners or family members communicate more
      openly, understand each other more deeply, and create a stronger, more
      compassionate connection.
    </p>
    <p>
      I offer sessions both in person at my Wellesley office and online
      statewide.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you’re struggling to find your way, figure out what’s next, or heal
      from past experiences, or just want to feel and live better, please <a
        href="/connect/">reach out</a
      > to discuss how I can help.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero-image {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 960px;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 40%;
  }
</style>
